caption.text: Today marks 113 years since the sinking of The Titanic. Liberty Science Center’s Titanic: The Artifact Exhibition lets you step back in time to experience what it was like aboard the “unsinkable ship”. This interactive exhibition features more than 130 real artifacts, authentic room re-creations, and a chilled 7-foot-tall iceberg replica you can actually touch! Thank you to LSC for letting me check out this premium exhibition before it sets sail September 1.

Read all about it on the site today (link in bio).

caption.text: As a Karate Kid fan, I’ve loved @CobraKaiSeries since it premiered on YouTube Red in 2018. I just finished watching the final episodes on Netflix and there were so many great full circle moments & poetic payoffs, and an overall satisfying ending to its 6 season run. So glad I got to meet the original Karate Kids, @William_Zabka & @Ralph_Macchio to get this comic signed & slabbed!
